2},6+5{x}^{2}+3x,6+6{x}^{2}+4x,\\\ 6+7{x}^{2}+3x,7+2x+6{x}
^{2},7+4x+7{x}^{2},\\\ 7+6{x}^{2}+3x,8+2x+7{x}^{2},8+6x+8{
x}^{2},8+8x+{x}^{2},
